	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div>
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la" type="auto">S.</s>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Reverende in Christo pater, cum tam certum haberem hominem, qui tuas mihi reddidisset, committere non potui, quin brevibus saltem te edocerem <persName type="auto_name">Lampertum</persName> illum, de quo scribis iam non esse ad urbem; itaque ea, quae cupis, expedire non potui; sed quam primum redierit, in id negocium inquiram.</s>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la" type="auto">De rebus <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l834" cert="high">Italicis</placeName> nihil certi habeo.</s>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Spero tibi binas meas redditas.</s>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><foreign xml:lang="de">Ich han by des Nülen sun, dem <persName type="auto_name">Hans Nülen</persName>, üch die letsten zuͦgeschickt</foreign> et omnino puto redditas, cum multum intersit te ea scire, quae scribuntur.</s>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Hodie hic fuerunt nobiscum nonnulli ministri ecclesiarum 10 Iurisdictionum a nobis evocati.</s>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Qui affirmant, quae a legatis in commitiis in gratiam <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2448" cert="high">Quinquepagicorum</placeName> essent facta, insciis communitatibus fieri.</s>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Itaque ego spero multos bonos posse melius instrui; ad hoc totum plurimum momenti afferret, si <placeName ref="l587" type="auto_name" cert="high">Tigurini</placeName> et reliqui modeste scriberent, de quo ante quoque ad te scripsi.</s>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Cum ruina nostra cum vestro malo sit coniuncta, non negligenter hoc totum negotium est administrandum.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="la" type="auto">De rebus <placeName ref="l522" cert="high">Venetis</placeName> proxime te edocui.</s>
					<s n="11" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Ex <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l822" cert="high">Germania</placeName> nos nihil, sed nec ex <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l832" cert="high">Gallia</placeName>.</s>
					<s n="12" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Quid <placeName ref="l18" cert="high">Augustę</placeName> fiat et in <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l832" cert="high">Gallia</placeName>, ex te scire avemus.</s>
					<s n="13" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Scripserat <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p252" cert="high">Bäldius</persName> pacem inter <persName cert="high" type="citizen_name" ref="p8282">Maximilianum</persName> et <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2510" cert="high">Turcam</placeName> esse confectam; sed <placeName ref="l28" cert="high">Basilea</placeName> diversum scribitur.</s>
					<s n="14" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Tu nos verum edoce, si per occupationes licet.</s>
					<s n="15" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Qui Venetiis veniunt, de longe maximo <placeName type="auto_name">Turcę</placeName> apparatu nunciant.</s>
					<s n="16" xml:lang="la" type="auto" ana="farewell">Vale, reverende in Christo pater.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="17" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName ref="l98" cert="high">Curię</placeName> 15. februarii anno 1566.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="18" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Tui observantissimus <persName ref="p8009" cert="high">Ioa[nnes] Fab[ricius</persName>].</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="19" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Amplissimo viro d. <persName ref="p495" type="citizen_name" cert="high">Heinrycho Bullingero</persName>, domino suo et in Christo patri reverendo.</s>
					<s n="20" xml:lang="de" type="auto"><placeName ref="l587" type="auto_name" cert="high">Zürich</placeName> an herren <persName ref="p495" type="citizen_name" cert="high">Bullinger</persName>.</s>
				</p>
